<section class="section">
  <div class="container split">
    <div class="flow measure">
      <p class="lead-first">Direct Interiors North West Limited, established in {{ site.estYear }} and based in Chester and North Wales, are specialists in the design and installation of industrial and commercial interiors throughout the North West and UK.</p>
      <p>Formerly known as <strong>Ceilings Direct North West Limited</strong> before a change of company name in February 2021 — the change of name was prompted by the increasing growth of our company and its expansion of trades within our team.</p>
      <p>Our design and installation teams are renowned for their professionalism, project focus and performance reliability. We’re proud of the reputation we’ve built over two decades.</p>
      <p>In an industry where efficiency is key, Direct Interiors offer experience, technical expertise, product intelligence and know-how within the field of commercial interior fit-outs and refurbishments.</p>
      <p>We have a track record of success and a diverse portfolio of completed interior fitting-out projects for offices, industrial premises and prestige residential projects.</p>
      <div class="about-actions">
